content: Last, a trend we've highlighted in prior quarters, revenue for active was up 13% over last year, as the mix of active accounts continues to improve, and we enjoy continued success in driving engagement and penetration over drafting the customer base, is worth noting that the growth of ARPU in our direct channels been growing at a higher rate than the overall consumer segment due to improving account mix, and direct customers have a higher annual revenue per active account than those in the retail channel.
